---
import Layout from "../layouts/Main.astro";
import Experience from "../components/Experience.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="animate-in">
    <h1>Hi there!</h1>
    <p>
      I'm Daniel, a Senior Full Stack Developer based in Amsterdam, working at <a
        class="text-primary cursor-pointer hover:underline"
        href="https://ipractice.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">iPractice</a
      >, a company focused on making mental health care accessible to everyone.
    </p>
    <p class="text-accent pt-8 text-base">
      I specialize in architecting, designing and developing scalable software solutions on Azure
      and AWS. I also use AI-driven tooling daily, from code reviews and monitoring to generating
      tests and scaffolding features.
    </p>
    <p class="text-accent pt-8 text-base">
      On the backend, I'm experienced in .NET, Go, Python and SQL. On the front, I'm experienced in
      TypeScript & JavaScript (React, Astro, Solid, HTMX). Most recently, I've been working with
      React Native and Expo. I use LLM tooling and automation heavily in my daily workflow, to stay
      fast and focus on the parts that actually need a human.
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr class="my-6 opacity-30 lg:my-20" />

  <section
    class="text-accent animate-in flex auto-cols-auto grid-flow-col flex-col gap-12 text-base lg:grid"
  >
    <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center">
      <img src="profile.png" class="w-[9vw] w-[150px] rounded-full" alt="Daniel Agg" />
      <!-- <div class="mt-6 w-fit lg:w-full">
        <Button
          label="Download my CV"
          onClick={() => window.open("/DanielAgg_CV.pdf")}
        />
      </div> -->
    </div>
    <section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <p>
        I advocate for modular monoliths with vertical slicing, Domain Driven Design, true CI/CD
        with Trunk Based Development and feature flags, fitness functions, procedural code and
        compartmentalizing volatile parts of our applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm passionate about researching adaptable software architectures, enabling applications to
        gracefully evolve over time: I came to realize the value of an adaptable architecture, which
        can facilitate the ever-changing landscape of business needs and keep the tempo of
        development rapid, without accumulating technical debt. I use AI tooling the same way: to
        automate code reviews, generate and maintain tests, triage production issues and turn
        repetitive engineering chores into prompts and pipelines.
      </p>
      <p>
        While I love geeking out over architectures, I like to think that I'm also pragmatic, always
        keeping in mind that my goal as a software developer is to deliver a working product, not
        the blueprint of it.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>

  <hr class="my-6 opacity-30 lg:mt-24 lg:mb-12" />

  <section class="animate-in">
    <h2 class="pb-6">Experience</h2>

    <div class="relative space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-primary/20 absolute top-6 bottom-6 left-[7px] w-px"></div>

      <div class="relative pl-8">
        <span
          class="bg-primary absolute top-2 left-0 size-3.5 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)]"
          style="animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;"></span>
        <Experience
          title="Senior Full Stack Developer"
          employer="iPractice"
          employerUrl="https://ipractice.com"
          location="Amsterdam, Netherlands"
          startDate={new Date("2023-12-01")}
          isCurrent
          description="I'm working on both internal and external applications for psychologists and their clientele. This includes apps to manage incoming referrals, invoices, appointment scheduling and online consults (chat & video)."
        />
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-8">
        <span
          class="border-primary/40 bg-background absolute top-2 left-[3px] size-2 rounded-full border"
        ></span>
        <Experience
          title="Senior Full Stack Developer"
          employer="Apiumhub"
          employerUrl="https://apiumhub.com"
          location="A Coruña, Spain"
          startDate={new Date("2021-04-01")}
          endDate={new Date("2023-11-01")}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-8">
        <span
          class="border-primary/40 bg-background absolute top-2 left-[3px] size-2 rounded-full border"
        ></span>
        <Experience
          title="Full Stack Developer"
          employer="Glownexus"
          employerUrl="https://www.glownexus.com/"
          location="Budapest, Hungary"
          startDate={new Date("2018-09-01")}
          endDate={new Date("2021-04-01")}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-8">
        <span
          class="border-primary/40 bg-background absolute top-2 left-[3px] size-2 rounded-full border"
        ></span>
        <Experience
          title="Junior/Medior .NET Developer"
          employer="Atos Consulting"
          employerUrl="https://atos.net/en/"
          location="Budapest, Hungary"
          startDate={new Date("2016-05-01")}
          endDate={new Date("2018-09-01")}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
